{"tid":2442366,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"公大生拆鐵欄罪成 官指不肯認錯 拒索服務令報告判更生中心","createTime":"2021-03-11T10:09:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T12:34:41.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"215f106eb25746c45bad809aa0995a517a14a9e6","tid":2442366,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:09:16.000Z","msg":"網⺠前年11月發起「三罷」 及「黎明行動」抗爭活動，大批市⺠響應號召。有公開大學男學生涉於上水拆毀路邊鐵欄，遭警員發現及拘捕。他早前被裁定刑事毀壞罪成，案件今判刑。辯方一度要求再為被告索取社會報務令報告，惟裁判官<span class=\"red\">黃國輝引述被告的感化官報告指，被告仍持否認錯誤的態度，故拒絕辯方要求，判被告進入更生中心</span>。被告進入囚室時，公眾席上多人向他呼叫：「撐住呀！」<br />\n<br />\n惟黃官指，被告破壞公共設施，拆掉欄杆，一旦馬路發生意外時，車輛有可能剷上行人路，對路人構成威脅。黃官又指破壞行為嚴重，適合判處監禁，並指報告顯示被告仍然持有否認錯誤的態度，不適宜判處社會服務令，故判被告進入更生中心，接受規律式訓練。"},{"pid":"bf2b003a79ac097d318502f6f053fad635250b54","tid":2442366,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:09:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210311/5X4EXN2JOVEBTNMRABT7LDMVF4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210311%2F5X4EXN2JOVEBTNMRABT7LDMVF4%2F&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHdWqQ%2Br5Wu6dnGlIIIMUdw0%3D&h=e52f8d84\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210311%2F5X4EXN2JOVEBTNMRABT7LDMVF4%2F&h=8a9f6f3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210311/5X4EXN2JOVEBTNMRABT7LDMVF4/</a>"},{"pid":"9bcfe98475fae0098fd456c16589b0a702143687","tid":2442366,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:10:44.000Z","msg":"寧死不屈嘅志氣..."},{"pid":"3e49375588442f76dd75d52add48ae125e01b234","tid":2442366,"uid":393145,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:12:03.000Z","msg":"又係呢啲作文, 一旦...一旦... 吹到去核爆毀滅地球啦"},{"pid":"1c98c98cf412c9ea0a84e85921e9441bba8c56cc","tid":2442366,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:13:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\